00:04:33.290 --> 00:04:35.490
And so I'm creating
a reputation,

00:04:35.490 --> 00:04:38.320
I'm creating a persona for
who I am in high school.

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:41.110
And there's two guys who are
in the grade above me, Sam

00:04:41.110 --> 00:04:42.490
and Steven.

00:04:42.490 --> 00:04:45.084
