00:08:42.850 --> 00:08:45.130
And my father had a
conversation of me,

00:08:45.130 --> 00:08:49.550
really pressing for me to share
what is going on in your life.

00:08:49.550 --> 00:08:52.850
And I told him I think I'm gay.

00:08:52.850 --> 00:08:56.810
I've been seeing other guys at
