00:09:18.930 --> 00:09:21.950
And he started searching in the
New York area for therapists.

00:09:21.950 --> 00:09:23.860
And he came across a
conversion therapist

00:09:23.860 --> 00:09:27.970
who told him, well, there is
no such thing as homosexuality.

00:09:27.970 --> 00:09:29.970
And it's all part
of childhood trauma.

00:09:29.970 --> 00:09:32.270
Everyone is born
innately heterosexual.

00:09:32.270 --> 00:09:35.050
And because your son is still
young and still inexperienced

00:09:35.050 --> 00:09:38.460
sexually, you'll start to see
his heterosexuality come back

00:09:38.460 --> 00:09:40.430
in six weeks.

00:09:40.430 --> 00:09:41.540
My dad was thrilled.

00:09:41.540 --> 00:09:44.030
He found an opportunity
of a lifetime.

00:09:44.030 --> 00:09:47.490
And so out of my fear of
ever getting hurt again,

00:09:47.490 --> 00:09:50.860
trusting my father,
and his love for me,

00:09:50.860 --> 00:09:53.854
I began conversion therapy.

00:09:53.854 --> 00:09:55.770
It was five years I was
in conversion therapy,

00:09:55.770 --> 00:09:57.728
so obviously, the six
weeks didn't really work.

00:10:00.950 --> 00:10:07.460
And just to really say what
conversion therapy was like.

00:10:07.460 --> 00:10:10.090
So you have to blame someone
in conversion therapy.

00:10:10.090 --> 00:10:12.960
If you're not born gay,
it came from somewhere.

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:15.870
So I had a really
fortunate upbringing.

00:10:15.870 --> 00:10:16.540
I had no trauma.

00:10:16.540 --> 00:10:17.810
My parents were great.

00:10:17.810 --> 00:10:18.900
They loved me.

00:10:18.900 --> 00:10:20.403
They spoiled me, if anything.

00:10:23.399 --> 00:10:24.440
But I had to look for it.

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:26.440
I'm the only son,
so the first guess

00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:29.636
was I have too much
female in my life.

00:10:29.636 --> 00:10:32.260
So what I had to do was I had to
spend as much time as possible

00:10:32.260 --> 00:10:34.135
with the other guys at
school, so I can learn

00:10:34.135 --> 00:10:35.680
about masculinity,
learn what it's

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:37.540
like to relate to other guys.

00:10:37.540 --> 00:10:40.130
Simultaneously, I had to
avoid women at all costs.

00:10:40.130 --> 00:10:43.230
These are the first steps
of curing homosexuality.

00:10:43.230 --> 00:10:46.050
[LAUGHTER]

00:10:46.050 --> 00:10:50.100
