00:50:20.300 --> 00:50:22.980
but we did every holiday, we
celebrated Shabbat dinners

00:50:22.980 --> 00:50:25.840
every Friday, but it was
really out of tradition.

00:50:25.840 --> 00:50:28.820
And my father was
this businessman.

00:50:28.820 --> 00:50:31.850
And he just saw no
possibility of me

00:50:31.850 --> 00:50:33.854
succeeding at all in
life, even though there's

00:50:33.854 --> 00:50:35.270
an overwhelming
amount of evidence

00:50:35.270 --> 00:50:39.410
that people can be openly gay
and succeed in their careers.

00:50:39.410 --> 00:50:42.480
He just felt like--
my father hustled.

00:50:42.480 --> 00:50:43.990
He's pretty much
an entrepreneur.

00:50:43.990 --> 00:50:46.590
Didn't have an education,
and he succeeded.

00:50:46.590 --> 00:50:49.600
And he felt like, there's no
way you're going to succeed.

00:50:49.600 --> 00:50:51.070
And if this is
just in your head,

00:50:51.070 --> 00:50:52.720
I'm going to help
