00:50:52.720 --> 00:50:54.710
And that was just
what he thought.

00:50:54.710 --> 00:50:58.290
He still sort of thinks that.

00:50:58.290 --> 00:51:01.250
I took the position to
love and accept him exactly

00:51:01.250 --> 00:51:04.100
the way he is, and
