are on the fence.

00:51:51.771 --> 00:51:54.020
This is something that has
been a pattern that I still

00:51:54.020 --> 00:51:55.740
haven't gotten rid of.

00:51:55.740 --> 00:51:57.770
And it's sort of like,
I see how clear it is,

00:51:57.770 --> 00:51:59.770
because of the field I'm
in and the world I came

00:51:59.770 --> 00:52:01.145
from being in
conversion therapy.

00:52:04.080 --> 00:52:07.550
Something like I always say,
you know, I can't pee for you.

00:52:07.550 --> 00:52:10.790
