able to do it on their own,

00:52:10.790 --> 00:52:11.950
if they ever choose to.

00:52:11.950 --> 00:52:13.950
If they want to have their
full self-expression,

00:52:13.950 --> 00:52:15.980
have their authenticity
to who they are.

00:52:15.980 --> 00:52:18.670
And as a friend,
just no matter what,

00:52:18.670 --> 00:52:21.180
love and knowledge
